    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presented is an exceptional 2004 BMW M3 (E46), a benchmark of atmospheric performance. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double VANOS, delivering a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. This example features the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission, ensuring an analog connection to the rear-mounted M Variable Differential Lock. The suspension geometry is factory-spec, maintaining precise turn-in and lateral stability. This vehicle is in museum-quality condition, with a flawless undercarriage and pristine exterior finish. A mechanically sorted, collector-grade icon for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 49500.0,
