      "description": "Offering a collector-grade BMW E46 M3, a superlative example of the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six powerplant. This vehicle features a meticulously maintained Double-VANOS system and individual throttle bodies for instantaneous atmospheric induction response. The chassis has been professionally reinforced at the rear subframe mounting points, and the rod bearing service is documented. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The suspension retains its factory-correct geometry with fresh bushings and Sachs dampers. With pristine paint depth and an interior free of bolster wear, this is a turn-key specimen for the uncompromising driver.",
